<p>The <code>open</code> tag outputs a literal opening brace.</p>

<h2>Escaping PAD Syntax</h2>
<pre>To show {open}$variable{close} literally:
{open}open{close}$variable{open}close{close}</pre>
<p>Result: {open}$variable{close}</p>

<h2>Documenting PAD Code</h2>
<pre>{open}open{close}if $count gt 0{open}close{close}
  Has items
{open}open{close}/if{open}close{close}</pre>
<p>Shows:</p>
<code>{open}if $count gt 0{close}<br>
  Has items<br>
{open}/if{close}</code>

<h2>Multiple Braces</h2>
<pre>{open}open{close}{open}open{close}nested{open}close{close}{open}close{close}</pre>
<p>Result: {open}{open}nested{close}{close}</p>
